        Splurting out unsolicited inspiration since 2015
      </div>
      <div class="col-5 links">
        <%= link_to 'Contribute', '#' %>
        <%= link_to 'About', '#' %>
      </div>
    </header>


<hr />

    <br class="clear" />

    <%= yield %>


  </body>
